TacoViz - Simple tool to visualize GW2 Tactical Overlay's POIs on a map image

Guild Wars 2 Tactical Overlay (https://gw2taco.blogspot.de/)

Requirements:
 - Perl modules:
  - Image::Size
  - LWP::Simple
  - XML::Simple
  - Math::ConvexHull
 - ImageMagick
 - TODO: Is the list complete?

Installation:
 - Just clone repository :)

Using TacoViz:
 - Calling showPOIs.pl with the path to the xml file containing POIs will generate a map image for each map with POIs.
 - showPOIs.pl <xmlfile>

Calibration of new map image:
 - ./calibrate.pl <mapId> <mapImagePath> <coordinates-of-wps> [<coordinates-of-wps>...]

Legal notes:
 - The map images in the maps directory are based on content in Guild Wars 2
